    <description>## The Taskmaster (Unseen Killer) - |Converted Prince|
**Passive: Royal Blood** 
 [Only usable upon the death of a king] As a Royal, you can put your name forward for nominations to become the next King. 

**Day Ability: Constrain**
Imprison a player in one of the underground prison that looks like Prince&#39;s prison at night, Occupying the target (Bypasses Occupy Immunity). 

**Day Ability: Bewilderment**
Shock a player that causes he can&#39;t speak and accusing anyone during the day.

**Night Ability: Haze**
If you will imprison same person next day you have 2 options to do:
1. You bully a player that causes him to leave a court for 2 days. He will come back to the court after these 2 days [Of course If game won&#39;t end earlier ). In this time person sees dead chat but he can&#39;t say anything. If physcian do &quot;Exhume&quot; it will shows that taskmaster did it. 
2. You bully a player that causes him to convert himself into unseen. If he&#39;s role can&#39;t be converted [That means only every neutral role]/ or there&#39;s too many unseen he changes automatically his role to your Mercenary. 

**Lore:** Once upon a time there was a king which had 2 childs. When he died a battle of throne had started. One of sons wanted so much to gain a title of king that he secretly killed his brother. Court found out what happened and didn&#39;t want to have king like him. So he was banished from the castle. Few months later he came back with fake personal data and had started live under the castle...

**Comments:** I think it would be really interesting role that could give a lot of fun :wink:</description>
    
